        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-mojo-600">
            <.icon name="hero-bell-alert" class=" text-white h-6 w-6" />
          </div>
          Tasks
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
          Know what to do and when to do it.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center items-center gap-x-6">
    <.link
      class="rounded-md bg-mojo-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-mojo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-mojo-600"
